This is how to check_dict_case of dict:
   Remember that i is 0
   Do this dict's length times:
      Remember that pair is item i in dict
      When pair's length is not 2, then:
         The answer is 0
      End when

      Remember that key is item 0 in pair
      Remember that value is item 1 in pair

      When isarray of key is no, then:
         The answer is 0
      End when
      When isarray of value is no, then:
         The answer is 0
      End when

      Increase i
   End do
   The answer is 1
